      "content": "that's a good start. can you expand on the part about why market forces alone aren't enough? i want to really hammer home the idea that the whole concept of \"meritocracy\" is basically a myth in this context because of these built-in biases. try to frame it so it's clear that relying on merit alone just ignores the systemic stuff you mentioned.",
